Skills.Name: Victorious Verse
Skills.Description: Raises own ATK by <color=red>{0}%</color> for 15s. Cancels all Shield effects on single enemy with highest ATK. Also inflicts 4-hit DMG (<color=red>{2}%</color> + <color=red>{3}%</color> + <color=red>{4}%</color> + <color=red>{5}%</color>). Further lowers Speed by {6}% for 10s.
Skills.ShortDescription: Raises own ATK. Cancels Shield effect(s), inflicts 4-hit DMG, lowers Speed of single enemy

Skills.Name: Guardian Angel
Skills.Description: Raises ATK of all allies by <color=red>{0}%</color> for 15s. Further shields DMG (<color=red>{1}%</color> of skill user's ATK) for 15s if Yellow Elemental.
Skills.ShortDescription: Raises ATK of all allies, shields DMG if Yellow Elemental

Skills.Name: Ancient Vanguard

Skills.ShortDescription: Cancels Shield effect(s), inflicts DMG on all enemies within range
